---
title: One-Pot Chicken & Silverbeet Dhal with Yoghurt
description: A no-fuss dhal sounds perfect right about now, so let’s whip one up in no time at all. You only need one pot and a whole lot of deliciousness - don’t worry, we have you covered. Add in red lentils, spiced chicken and veggies in a creamy tomato curry sauce and there you go. Dinner is served!
